Lets Change the Template and add some dynamic data.

DataBinding: -> Communication between your TS Code and your template

There are various methods of Data binding:

1. For outputting data on template:

    Business Logic (TS Code) ---------------> Template (HTML)

    a. String Interpolation {{data}}
    b. property Binding [property]="data"

2. Triggering on click ie react to user events 

    Business Logic (TS Code) <--------------- Template (HTML)   {Reverse Direction}

    a. Event Binding --> (event)="expression"

3. Reacting events and output at the same time (Two Way data Binding):
    Business Logic (TS Code) ---------------> Template (HTML)
    Business Logic (TS Code) <--------------- Template (HTML)

    a. [(ngModel)]="data"
